name: Elysium Shift, L.O.S.T and The Orchard live in Stafford!
description:
That's right y'all, Elysium Shift simply can't get enough of lobbing drop C ballistics at the walls of The Grapes in Stafford and are returning to finish the place off. 

Joined by fellow ear wax generators L.O.S.T as well as balls out, five a day, fret fuckers The Orchard! You don't wanna miss this one!

**Please make sure you keep a copy of your receipt to claim your ticket on the night**
